lines.text: They're from the other side of the tracks, and I don't want to get run over crossing!
Yeah, I'm a wolf in "ships" clothing!
Can't understand why they reject guys with flat feet and take em with flat heads!
Say there is a movie playing Maisie Goes to the Laundry.
No please, she gives me a headache. Ann Southern starred in the Maisie film series which makes this quote laughable.
